<HEADLINE> Tehran Stock Exchange Index up by 2.09 Points </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
TEHRAN, September 21 (Xinhua) -- The general price index at
Tehran Stock Exchange closed at 1,527.14 points on Monday, up
2.09 points compared to the figure on Sunday.
</P>
