<HEADLINE> Istanbul Stock Exchange Index Down </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
ANKARA, September 21 (Xinhua) -- Turkey's Istanbul Stock
Exchange National-100 Index closed at 2,141.65 on Monday, down
136.68 points from Friday's finish.
</P>
<P>
The trading was active with the turnover reaching over 76
trillion Turkish Liras (over 277 million U.S. dollars).
</P>
<P>
The financial index went down 200.43 points, or 7.11 percent,
to close at 2,665.14 points, the industrial index fell 70.68
points to close at 1,788.71 points and the service index dropped
169.30 points to close at 2,588.91 points. 
</P>
