<HEADLINE> Clinton: Campaign Against Terrorism Should Be at </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
UNITED NATIONS, September 21 (Xinhua) -- U.S. President Bill
Clinton Monday called on the world to put the fight against
terrorism at the top of its agenda.
</P>
<P>
Clinton stressed that the cause of terrorism was not a conflict
between Islamic civilization and the West.
</P>
<P>
Addressing at the general debate of the 53rd session of the
