<HEADLINE> Japanese Empress Cancels India Visit </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
NEW DELHI, September 22 (Xinhua) -- Japanese Empress Michiko
has canceled her planned visit to India on the government's advice
in view of India's nuclear tests.
</P>
<P>
