<HEADLINE> Senior Chinese Leader Meets With Angolan PLM Members </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
BEIJING, September 22 (Xinhua) -- Vice President Hu Jintao, in
a meeting today with an Angolan delegation led by Lopo
Donascimento, general secretary of the People's Liberation
Movement (PLM) of Angola, said that, thanks to stable bilateral
relations, cooperation in economic, cultural and other areas
between China and Angola has seen good development since the two
formed diplomatic ties 15 years ago.
</P>
