<HEADLINE> German President Ends Visit to Mongolia </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
ULAN BATOR, September 22 (Xinhua) -- Mongolian President
Nachagyn Bagabandy said that his country needs help from Germany
to develop relations with the European Union (EU) and the North
Atlantic Treaty Organization (NATO).
</P>
