<HEADLINE> Tang Jiaxuan Meets with Brazilian FM </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
UNITED NATIONS, September 21 (Xinhua) -- Chinese Foreign
Minister Tang Jiaxuan on Monday held talks with Felipe Palmeira
Lampreia, Brazil's Minister of Foreign Affairs.
</P>
<P>
During the meeting, Tang Jiaxuan, who is here to attend the
53rd session of the General Assembly, recalled that the heads of
China and Brazil reached consensus in 1993 on establishing
strategic partnership between the two countries, the first such
relationship between China and a country from Latin America.
</P>
