Lampreia, also attending the 53rd session of the General
Assembly, said bilateral cooperation in all fields continued to
deepen over the past 25 years and Brazil was fully satisfied with
it.
</P>
<P>
He congratulated China on its great achievements in its economy
and appreciated the role it had played in the financial crisis in
Asia. 
